    <h1 class="opener__hed  -is-over-bg opener__hed--light opener__hed--small" >        The Ghosts of John Tanton
    </h1>

            <h2 class="opener__dek  -is-over-bg opener__dek--light" style="display: none" >            Climate change and anti-immigrant hate are colliding, foretelling a volatile future.
        </h2>
    
            <div class="article-meta-1  -is-over-bg article-meta-1--light">
            <span class="article-meta-1__byline">
                by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/abrahm-lustgarten">Abrahm Lustgarten</a>            </span>
            <time class="article-meta-1__pubdate">
                <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-10-19EDT05:00">Oct. 19, 5 a.m. EDT</time>
            </time>
