<div class="highlights">
    <h3 class="highlights__heading">Reporting Highlights</h3>
    <ul class="highlights__list">
                    <li class="highlights__highlight"><span class="highlights__subheading">Tanton’s Network: </span> Today’s contentious immigration debate is the construct of one man’s effort to halt overpopulation, brace for climate change and preserve “European” culture.</li>
            <li class="highlights__highlight"><span class="highlights__subheading">Green Hate: </span> Now climate change is amplifying environmental concerns that have always run through the white supremacy and the anti-immigration movements.</li>
            <li class="highlights__highlight"><span class="highlights__subheading">Eco-Fascism: </span> Experts warn that extremists who seize on global warming to justify violence are part of a far right trend to reclaim environmentalism as their own.</li>
            </ul>
    <p class="highlights__disclaimer">
        These highlights were written by the reporters and editors who worked on this story. <span id="survey-placeholder"></span>
    </p>
</div>

